Package com.qualcomm.phub.api.v1.deckofcards

Interface Summary
DeckOfCardsManager Fundamental methods required by a manager.
 

Class Summary
Card An abstract representation of a card.
DeckOfCards A programmatic representation of a deck of cards.
DeckOfCardsIcon A deck of cards icon, as displayed on the home page of the watch.
ListCard A representation of a list of cards.
NotifyTextCard An individual card.
RemoteDeckOfCards A specialised deck of cards implementation for 3rd party apps to install, update and uninstall.
RemoteDeckOfCardsIcon A specialised deck of cards icon implementation for 3rd party apps.
RemoteToqNotification A specialised Toq notification implementation for 3rd party apps.
ToqNotification A Toq notification which can be sent to the watch, resulting in a pop-up and a new or updated card in the Notification deck of cards app.
 

Exception Summary
DeckOfCardsException Deck of cards exception.
RemoteDeckOfCardsException A specialised deck of cards exception for 3rd party apps.
